snippet.title: YOU DON'T KNOW JACK on Facebook
snippet.description:
Play the game! http://apps.facebook.com/youdontknowjack

We wanted to make a video about elephants playing elephant soccer and one of the elephants accidentally stepping on a monkey referee, but we couldn't wait around any longer for it to happen, so we made this trailer video for YDKJ on Facebook instead.
